title: Conte happy with performance, says Chelsea have a chance to win tie
text:
Conte happy with performance, says Chelsea have a chance to win tie 2:55am GMT - 00:59 
Chelsea manager Antonio Conte says his side played well against Barcelona in the Champions League tie first leg, saying the performance gives them confidence they can win the tie overall. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
